!isdllfuncenabled(201) &minvalenabled
enable &minvalenabled
    Move &minvalenabled to $minvalenabled
    From bpdllfc
    Where functionid = 201
End-Select
Move 1 to #nullbuyer
Move '' to $DefaultBuyer
